It looks like the aggregate scores db query for grpo is being slow and causing get_weights to take long time for valis. The current db index works for success = true queries but the grpo query just checks for score != null, so a new index is needed:
```
CREATE INDEX ix_results_env_hotkey_rev_score_null 
ON affine_results (env_name, hotkey, revision) 
INCLUDE (score) 
WHERE score IS NOT NULL;
```
can also just make a generic index like:
```
CREATE INDEX ix_results_env_hotkey_rev
ON affine_results (env_name, hotkey, revision);
```
